raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: brain-isotopic-distribution
  version: "1.5.19"

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/brain_isotopic_distribution-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: cad44fcb1ddbd26787dafb65345558df5119a7928b6e773fbb9dd5fd4f3334de

build:
  number: 1
  script: ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - cython

    - ${{ compiler("c") }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
  host:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - wheel
    - cython
    - pip
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - brainpy
      pip_check: true
  - requirements:
      run:
        - pytest
    files:
      source:
        - tests/
    script:
      - pytest tests/

about:
  summary: Fast and efficient theoretical isotopic profile generation
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  homepage: https://github.com/mobiusklein/brainpy
  repository: https://github.com/mobiusklein/brainpy
  documentation: http://mobiusklein.github.io

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bgruening
    - hadim
